FBIS3-31011 "dreeu030_i_94014" FBIS-EEU-94-030 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Feb 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA Gvero: Aid Workers To Share Fate of Serbs AU1102104094 Cologne Deutschlandfunk Network in German 1000 GMT 11 Feb 94 AU1102104094 Cologne Deutschlandfunk Network Language: German Article Type:BFN [Text] The deputy chief of the general staff of the Bosnian Serbs, Gvero, has threatened the employees of relief organizations with reprisals in the event of NATO air strikes. At a news conference northeast of the besieged capital city, the general said that then the aid workers would have to share the fate of the Bosnian Serbs. They would not be permitted to leave.
